class Solution:
    def minimumSum(self, grid: List[List[int]]) -> int:
        m, n = len(grid), len(grid[0])
        def f(top, bottom, left, right):
            a, b, c, d = bottom - 1, top, right - 1, left
            for i in range(top, bottom):
                for j in range(left, right):
                    if grid[i][j] == 1:
                        a = min(a, i)
                        b = max(b, i)
                        c = min(c, j)
                        d = max(d, j)
            area = (b - a + 1) * (d - c + 1)
            return (a, b, c, d, area)
        a, b, c, d, area = f(0, m, 0, n)
        # print(a, b, c, d, area)
        ret = area
        for t in range(a + 1, b + 1):
            a1, b1, c1, d1, area1 = f(a, t, c, d + 1)
            a2, b2, c2, d2, area2 = f(t, b + 1, c, d + 1)
            # print("i:", i, a1, b1, c1, d1, area1)
            # print("i:", i, a2, b2, c2, d2, area2)
            for i in range(a1 + 1, b1 + 1):
                a11, b11, c11, d11, area11 = f(a1, i, c1, d1 + 1)
                a12, b12, c12, d12, area12 = f(i, b1 + 1, c1, d1 + 1)
                ret = min(ret, area2 + area11 + area12)
            for i in range(a2 + 1, b2 + 1):
                a21, b21, c21, d21, area21 = f(a2, i, c2, d2 + 1)
                a22, b22, c22, d22, area22 = f(i, b2 + 1, c2, d2 + 1)
                ret = min(ret, area1 + area21 + area22)
            for j in range(c1 + 1, d1 + 1):
                a11, b11, c11, d11, area11 = f(a1, b1 + 1, c1, j)
                a12, b12, c12, d12, area12 = f(a1, b1 + 1, j, d1 + 1)
                ret = min(ret, area2 + area11 + area12)
            for j in range(c2 + 1, d2 + 1):
                a21, b21, c21, d21, area21 = f(a2, b2 + 1, c2, j)
                a22, b22, c22, d22, area22 = f(a2, b2 + 1, j, d2 + 1)
                ret = min(ret, area1 + area21 + area22)
        for t in range(c + 1, d + 1):
            a1, b1, c1, d1, area1 = f(a, b + 1, c, t)
            a2, b2, c2, d2, area2 = f(a, b + 1, t, d + 1)
            # print("j:", j, a1, b1, c1, d1, area1)
            # print("j:", j, a2, b2, c2, d2, area2)
            for i in range(a1 + 1, b1 + 1):
                a11, b11, c11, d11, area11 = f(a1, i, c1, d1 + 1)
                a12, b12, c12, d12, area12 = f(i, b1 + 1, c1, d1 + 1)
                ret = min(ret, area2 + area11 + area12)
            for i in range(a2 + 1, b2 + 1):
                a21, b21, c21, d21, area21 = f(a2, i, c2, d2 + 1)
                a22, b22, c22, d22, area22 = f(i, b2 + 1, c2, d2 + 1)
                ret = min(ret, area1 + area21 + area22)
            for j in range(c1 + 1, d1 + 1):
                a11, b11, c11, d11, area11 = f(a1, b1 + 1, c1, j)
                a12, b12, c12, d12, area12 = f(a1, b1 + 1, j, d1 + 1)
                ret = min(ret, area2 + area11 + area12)
            for j in range(c2 + 1, d2 + 1):
                a21, b21, c21, d21, area21 = f(a2, b2 + 1, c2, j)
                a22, b22, c22, d22, area22 = f(a2, b2 + 1, j, d2 + 1)
                ret = min(ret, area1 + area21 + area22)
        return ret
